        "message": "Patch Set 11:\n\n> what is the problem with helm image here? This series of commits\n > should not touch helm and I saw no place where it does\n\nthis commit was only intended to store somewhere rke-related images - how and where it should be integrated is out-of-scope of this series of commits at least until the download/preparation stage of installer is finished, helm images should be the same as before with rancher, rke is not concerned with this",
